{"tid":1847122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身邊得港豬朋友真係好撚辛苦","createTime":"2020-01-28T02:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T02:24:11.000Z","uid":61923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eed37bd11eee64db31aac3da0b942ef1e0ada1ba","tid":1847122,"uid":61923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T02:20:49.000Z","msg":"平時身邊啲朋友好多唔係港豬就係左膠<br />\n遊行淨係識去打卡post相，post完就走先個啲<br />\n仲要成日聽到某啲friend話自己係前線去溝女<br />\n琴日kobe死咗（利申無睇開籃球）成個ig都係kobe<br />\n我就唔明點解我哋手足比人殺比人姦<br />\n點解可以無人關注？<br />\n我都知kobe既影響力好大，好多人尊重佢<br />\n但係我哋手足拎條命出嚟，係咪更加應該比你哋尊重？<br />\n之後我仲要比哂我啲friend屌我唔尊重kobe<br />\n又話我on9 on9點點點<br />\n唉我好撚辛苦啊，到底有冇人會明白我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3f4bfb42947d900c79a4f964a6bc1689490587","tid":1847122,"uid":61923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T02:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8192d81d86b13982f57a4df31d8d39ee36c377b6","tid":1847122,"uid":61923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T02:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9d182b415c3db933038d8cd9d839fe39c8d102","tid":1847122,"uid":61923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T02:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8a4dfb11a1d5e49bd06ff721cc570be9fefb9c","tid":1847122,"uid":316420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T02:24:11.000Z","msg":"加油 我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個frd 6-8月去足遊行 有買物資<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢同我講想食元氣"}]}